            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Because if you look at the languages actually used by the workforce, it paints a very different picture:</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
